claim.claim-text:
20. A hardware computer storage medium storing computer readable instructions which, when executed by a computer, cause the computer to perform steps, comprising:
running a business related application;
receiving, from the business related application, an instruction to display a typographic icon representing an entity of the business related application, the entity having a textual label comprising text;
displaying, on a display screen of a mobile device, a display portion of the typographic icon with a size that precludes display of an entirety of the text in the textual label, in a first font size, at one time; and
dynamically displaying the entirety of the text in the textual label in the display portion of the icon.
